Simple example for sobel test

x1 = rnorm(100)
m1 = -x1*0.5 + rnorm(100)*0.05
y1 = m1 + rnorm(100)*0.05
mediation.test( m1, x1, y1)
##                 Sobel        Aroian       Goodman
## z.value -1.043561e+01 -1.043523e+01 -1.043599e+01
## p.value  1.705179e-25  1.711967e-25  1.698416e-25
sobel(x1, m1, y1)

Mediation test on Gflex <t0 < RFlex

library(mediation)
## Loading required package: Matrix
## Loading required package: mvtnorm
## Loading required package: sandwich
## mediation: Causal Mediation Analysis
## Version: 4.4.6
#set.seed(20170801)
report$log10GompRFlex = log10(report$GompRFlex)

med.fit = lm(t0 ~ log10GompRFlex, data=report)  #mediator ~ treatment
summary(med.fit)
## 
## Call:
## lm(formula = t0 ~ log10GompRFlex, data = report)
## 
## Residuals:
##     Min      1Q  Median      3Q     Max 
## -10.487  -7.989   0.089   1.192  22.037 
## 
## Coefficients:
##                Estimate Std. Error t value Pr(>|t|)    
## (Intercept)     102.576     20.236   5.069 0.000215 ***
## log10GompRFlex   21.120      7.414   2.849 0.013693 *  
## ---
## Signif. codes:  0 '***' 0.001 '**' 0.01 '*' 0.05 '.' 0.1 ' ' 1
## 
## Residual standard error: 9.873 on 13 degrees of freedom
## Multiple R-squared:  0.3843, Adjusted R-squared:  0.337 
## F-statistic: 8.115 on 1 and 13 DF,  p-value: 0.01369
out.fit = lm(GompGFlex ~ t0 + log10GompRFlex, data=report)  #outcome ~ mediator + treatment
summary(out.fit)
## 
## Call:
## lm(formula = GompGFlex ~ t0 + log10GompRFlex, data = report)
## 
## Residuals:
##       Min        1Q    Median        3Q       Max
